{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.1","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:1","prev_osis_id":"Rom.007.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Point de condamnation pour ceux qui sont en J\u00e9sus-Christ. Ils marchent selon l\u2019esprit et non selon la chair, \u2014 \u00e9tant soutenus au milieu des souffrances du temps pr\u00e9sent, vivant dans l\u2019attente du salut, et ayant l\u2019assurance que rien ne peut les s\u00e9parer de l\u2019amour de Dieu en J\u00e9sus-Christ<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-11: cf. (Ga 3:13, 14. Ro 6:22, 23.) Ga 5:17-25; 6:8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Il n\u2019y a donc maintenant aucune condamnation pour ceux qui sont en J\u00e9sus-Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.2","name":"Romains 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.7.25","name":"Romains 7:25","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.7.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.2","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:2","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>En effet, la loi de l\u2019esprit de vie en J\u00e9sus-Christ m\u2019a affranchi de la loi du p\u00e9ch\u00e9 et de la mort.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.3","name":"Romains 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.1","name":"Romains 8:1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.3","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:3","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Car chose impossible \u00e0 la loi, parce que la chair la rendait sans force, Dieu a condamn\u00e9 le p\u00e9ch\u00e9 dans la chair, en envoyant, \u00e0 cause du p\u00e9ch\u00e9, son propre Fils dans une chair semblable \u00e0 celle du p\u00e9ch\u00e9,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.4","name":"Romains 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.2","name":"Romains 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.4","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:4","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>et cela afin que la justice de la loi f\u00fbt accomplie en nous, qui marchons, non selon la chair, mais selon l\u2019esprit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.5","name":"Romains 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.3","name":"Romains 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.5","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:5","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ceux, en effet, qui vivent selon la chair, s\u2019affectionnent aux choses de la chair, tandis que ceux qui vivent selon l\u2019esprit s\u2019affectionnent aux choses de l\u2019esprit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.6","name":"Romains 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.4","name":"Romains 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.6","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:6","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Et l\u2019affection de la chair, c\u2019est la mort, tandis que l\u2019affection de l\u2019esprit, c\u2019est la vie et la paix;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.7","name":"Romains 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.5","name":"Romains 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.7","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:7","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>car l\u2019affection de la chair est inimiti\u00e9 contre Dieu, parce qu\u2019elle ne se soumet pas \u00e0 la loi de Dieu, et qu\u2019elle ne le peut m\u00eame pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.8","name":"Romains 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.6","name":"Romains 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.8","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:8","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Or ceux qui vivent selon la chair ne sauraient plaire \u00e0 Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.9","name":"Romains 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.7","name":"Romains 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.9","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:9","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Pour vous, vous ne vivez pas selon la chair, mais selon l\u2019esprit, si du moins l\u2019Esprit de Dieu habite en vous. Si quelqu\u2019un n\u2019a pas l\u2019Esprit de Christ, il ne lui appartient pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.10","name":"Romains 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.8","name":"Romains 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.10","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:10","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Et si Christ est en vous, le corps, il est vrai, est mort \u00e0 cause du p\u00e9ch\u00e9, mais l\u2019esprit est vie \u00e0 cause de la justice.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.11","name":"Romains 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.9","name":"Romains 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.11","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:11","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et si l\u2019Esprit de celui qui a ressuscit\u00e9 J\u00e9sus d\u2019entre les morts habite en vous, celui qui a ressuscit\u00e9 Christ d\u2019entre les morts rendra aussi la vie \u00e0 vos corps mortels par son Esprit qui habite en vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.12","name":"Romains 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.10","name":"Romains 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.12","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:12","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-27: cf. Col 3:1-6. Ga 4:4-7. (1 Jn 3:1-3. 2 Co 4:16-18; 5:1-5. 2 Pi 3:13.) Jud v. 20, 21.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Ainsi donc, fr\u00e8res, nous ne sommes point redevables \u00e0 la chair, pour vivre selon la chair.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.13","name":"Romains 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.11","name":"Romains 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.13","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:13","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Si vous vivez selon la chair, vous mourrez; mais si par l\u2019Esprit vous faites mourir les actions du corps, vous vivrez,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.14","name":"Romains 8:14","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.12","name":"Romains 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.14","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:14","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>car tous ceux qui sont conduits par l\u2019Esprit de Dieu sont fils de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.15","name":"Romains 8:15","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.13","name":"Romains 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.15","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:15","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Et vous n\u2019avez point re\u00e7u un esprit de servitude, pour \u00eatre encore dans la crainte; mais vous avez re\u00e7u un Esprit d\u2019adoption, par lequel nous crions: Abba! P\u00e8re!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.16","name":"Romains 8:16","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.14","name":"Romains 8:14","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.16","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:16","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>L\u2019Esprit lui-m\u00eame rend t\u00e9moignage \u00e0 notre esprit que nous sommes enfants de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.17","name":"Romains 8:17","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.15","name":"Romains 8:15","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.17","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:17","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Or, si nous sommes enfants, nous sommes aussi h\u00e9ritiers: h\u00e9ritiers de Dieu, et coh\u00e9ritiers de Christ, si toutefois nous souffrons avec lui, afin d\u2019\u00eatre glorifi\u00e9s avec lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.18","name":"Romains 8:18","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.16","name":"Romains 8:16","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.18","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:18","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>J\u2019estime que les souffrances du temps pr\u00e9sent ne sauraient \u00eatre compar\u00e9es \u00e0 la gloire \u00e0 venir qui sera r\u00e9v\u00e9l\u00e9e pour nous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.19","name":"Romains 8:19","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.17","name":"Romains 8:17","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.19","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:19","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Aussi la cr\u00e9ation attend-elle avec un ardent d\u00e9sir la r\u00e9v\u00e9lation des fils de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.20","name":"Romains 8:20","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.18","name":"Romains 8:18","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.20","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:20","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Car la cr\u00e9ation a \u00e9t\u00e9 soumise \u00e0 la vanit\u00e9, non de son gr\u00e9, mais \u00e0 cause de celui qui l\u2019y a soumise,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.21","name":"Romains 8:21","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.19","name":"Romains 8:19","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.21","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:21","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>avec l\u2019esp\u00e9rance qu\u2019elle aussi sera affranchie de la servitude de la corruption, pour avoir part \u00e0 la libert\u00e9 de la gloire des enfants de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.22","name":"Romains 8:22","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.20","name":"Romains 8:20","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.22","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:22","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Or, nous savons que, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour, la cr\u00e9ation tout enti\u00e8re soupire et souffre les douleurs de l\u2019enfantement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.23","name":"Romains 8:23","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.21","name":"Romains 8:21","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.23","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:23","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Et ce n\u2019est pas elle seulement; mais nous aussi, qui avons les pr\u00e9mices de l\u2019Esprit, nous aussi nous soupirons en nous-m\u00eames, en attendant l\u2019adoption, la r\u00e9demption de notre corps.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.24","name":"Romains 8:24","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.22","name":"Romains 8:22","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.24","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:24","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Car c\u2019est en esp\u00e9rance que nous sommes sauv\u00e9s. Or, l\u2019esp\u00e9rance qu\u2019on voit n\u2019est plus esp\u00e9rance: ce qu\u2019on voit, peut-on l\u2019esp\u00e9rer encore?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.25","name":"Romains 8:25","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.23","name":"Romains 8:23","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.25","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:25","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Mais si nous esp\u00e9rons ce que nous ne voyons pas, nous l\u2019attendons avec pers\u00e9v\u00e9rance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.26","name":"Romains 8:26","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.24","name":"Romains 8:24","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.26","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:26","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>De m\u00eame aussi l\u2019Esprit nous aide dans notre faiblesse, car nous ne savons pas ce qu\u2019il nous convient de demander dans nos pri\u00e8res. Mais l\u2019Esprit lui-m\u00eame interc\u00e8de par des soupirs inexprimables;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.27","name":"Romains 8:27","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.25","name":"Romains 8:25","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.27","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:27","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>et celui qui sonde les c\u0153urs conna\u00eet quelle est la pens\u00e9e de l\u2019Esprit, parce que c\u2019est selon Dieu qu\u2019il interc\u00e8de en faveur des saints.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.28","name":"Romains 8:28","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.26","name":"Romains 8:26","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.28","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:28","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.029,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 28-39: cf. \u00c9p 1:3-12. (Ro 5:1-11. \u00c9s 50:8, 9. Jn 10:27-30.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Nous savons, du reste, que toutes choses concourent au bien de ceux qui aiment Dieu, de ceux qui sont appel\u00e9s selon son dessein.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.29","name":"Romains 8:29","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.27","name":"Romains 8:27","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.29","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:29","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Car ceux qu\u2019il a connus d\u2019avance, il les a aussi pr\u00e9destin\u00e9s \u00e0 \u00eatre semblables \u00e0 l\u2019image de son Fils, afin que son Fils f\u00fbt le premier-n\u00e9 entre plusieurs fr\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.30","name":"Romains 8:30","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.28","name":"Romains 8:28","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.30","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:30","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Et ceux qu\u2019il a pr\u00e9destin\u00e9s, il les a aussi appel\u00e9s; et ceux qu\u2019il a appel\u00e9s, il les a aussi justifi\u00e9s; et ceux qu\u2019il a justifi\u00e9s, il les a aussi glorifi\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.31","name":"Romains 8:31","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.29","name":"Romains 8:29","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.31","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:31","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Que dirons-nous donc \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard de ces choses? Si Dieu est pour nous, qui sera contre nous?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.32","name":"Romains 8:32","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.30","name":"Romains 8:30","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.32","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:32","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Lui, qui n\u2019a point \u00e9pargn\u00e9 son propre Fils, mais qui l\u2019a livr\u00e9 pour nous tous, comment ne nous donnera-t-il pas aussi toutes choses avec lui?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.33","name":"Romains 8:33","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.31","name":"Romains 8:31","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.33","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:33","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Qui accusera les \u00e9lus de Dieu? C\u2019est Dieu qui justifie!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.34","name":"Romains 8:34","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.32","name":"Romains 8:32","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.34","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:34","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Qui les condamnera? Christ est mort; bien plus, il est ressuscit\u00e9, il est \u00e0 la droite de Dieu, et il interc\u00e8de pour nous!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.35","name":"Romains 8:35","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.33","name":"Romains 8:33","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.35","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:35","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Qui nous s\u00e9parera de l\u2019amour de Christ? Sera-ce la tribulation, ou l\u2019angoisse, ou la pers\u00e9cution, ou la faim, ou la nudit\u00e9, ou le p\u00e9ril, ou l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.36","name":"Romains 8:36","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.34","name":"Romains 8:34","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.36","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:36","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>selon qu\u2019il est \u00e9crit:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    C\u2019est \u00e0 cause de toi qu\u2019on nous met \u00e0 mort tout le jour,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qu\u2019on nous regarde comme des brebis destin\u00e9es \u00e0 la boucherie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.37","name":"Romains 8:37","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.35","name":"Romains 8:35","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.37","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:37","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Mais dans toutes ces choses nous sommes plus que vainqueurs par celui qui nous a aim\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.38","name":"Romains 8:38","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.36","name":"Romains 8:36","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.38","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:38","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.008.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Car j\u2019ai l\u2019assurance que ni la mort ni la vie, ni les anges ni les dominations, ni les choses pr\u00e9sentes ni les choses \u00e0 venir,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.39","name":"Romains 8:39","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.37","name":"Romains 8:37","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.39","label":"","reference":"Romains 8:39","prev_osis_id":"Rom.008.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.009.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Rom.8.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>ni les puissances, ni la hauteur, ni la profondeur, ni aucune autre cr\u00e9ature ne pourra nous s\u00e9parer de l\u2019amour de Dieu manifest\u00e9 en J\u00e9sus-Christ notre Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.8","name":"Romains 8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.9.1","name":"Romains 9:1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.9.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.8.38","name":"Romains 8:38","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.8.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbfd04157.61974261');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbfd04157.61974261\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbfd04157.61974261","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbfd04157.61974261'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbfd04157.61974261\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}